    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>简单的计算器(C语言)</title>
    <link href="/2025/01/26/%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%99%A8-C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/"/>
    <url>/2025/01/26/%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%99%A8-C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p>这篇文章使用C语言实现了一个简单的计算器, 不过目前只能计算两数的加减乘除运算, 没有加入多个数运算和括号的机制, 后续可能会加上。<br>成为更强大的计算器</p><h1 id="Preview"><a href="#Preview" class="headerlink" title="Preview"></a>Preview</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ ./calc<br>&gt; 1+2<br>3<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h1><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> formula[<span class="hljs-keyword">sizeof</span> (<span class="hljs-type">char</span>*)];<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&gt; &quot;</span>);<span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>, formula);<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> left = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, right = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, res;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> symbol;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>* n = &amp;left;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">char</span>* ptr = &amp;formula[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];*ptr != <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;ptr++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span> &lt;= *ptr &amp;&amp; *ptr &lt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>            *n = <span class="hljs-number">10</span> * *n + (*ptr - <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>);<br>        &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (*ptr == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;+&#x27;</span>||*ptr == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>||*ptr == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;*&#x27;</span>||*ptr == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>            symbol = *ptr;<br>            n = &amp;right;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (symbol) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;+&#x27;</span>:<br>            res = left + right;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>:<br>            res = left - right;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;*&#x27;</span>:<br>            res = left * right;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (right != <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>                res = left / right;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Error: Divide by Zero\n&quot;</span>);<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">goto</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">exit</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>:<br>            res = left;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, res);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">exit</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
